# Changelog

All notable changes to the **CIMA GitHub Frontpage (c-hydro.github.io)** are documented in this file.

This project follows a simplified version of
[Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/)
and uses semantic versioning where applicable.

---

## [2.0.0] â€“ Current release

### Added
- New curated website structure organized by **domain areas**: Hydrology & Forecasting, Drought, and Other tools
- Explicit **tag-based classification rule** (`#hydrology`, `#drought`, default to Other)
- Reference workflow page describing typical model and analysis pipelines

### Changed
- Replaced dynamic GitHub API catalogue with a **static, curated card-based layout**
- Visual redesign aligned with **CIMA Foundation identity**

---

## [1.5.0]

### Added
- Card-based visualization of repositories
- Automatic listing of repositories using GitHub API (public repositories only)

### Changed
- Repositories displayed without explicit ordering or domain grouping

### Limitations
- No domain classification or tagging logic applied

---

## [1.0.0]

### Added
- Initial GitHub Pages frontpage
- Minimal presentation of CIMA GitHub repositories

### Notes
- No structured content or repository descriptions
- Served as a placeholder landing page

---
